  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients included in the study are treated at the Klinik f√ºr Neurochirurgie USZ. The clinical
      course is documented at Paraplegikerzentrum Balgrist using validated diagnostic procedures
      (e.g. SCIM, ASIA, neurophysiology).

      Study aims:

      Prognostic value of clinical diagnosis and additional diagnostic procedures? Which parameters
      exhibit optimal prognostic power? Differences between tumor/AVM associated lesions and
      traumatic lesions? What can we learn for pathophysiology and treatment?

        -  Trial with surgical intervention
    </textblock>
